Example: If I'm in Necro/Guard and a Lamentation drops. The warrior in the group is using Wurmslayer [aka Crap.]<br>
If everyone goes all/all on it, I won't sit out on the random but I will say that if I win, I am defaulting to the warrior. I see this as giving that person with crap gear an extra chance of winning something they can use. Nobody I've ever grouped with has had an issue with me doing it either. Or if they did, they didn't say anything. These people wanted all/all, it is mine to do what I want with if I win and that includes passing the item to someone else in the group who I think needs it.<br>
